---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | OpsForge Labs"
  description="About OpsForge Labs — hands-on DevOps training, real infrastructure exposure, and AI-powered operations for production-ready engineers."
  active="about"
>
  <main>
    <header class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-label">About OpsForge Labs</p>
        <h1>Bridge theory and <span class="gradient-text">enterprise engineering</span></h1>
        <p>
          OpsForge Labs was created to bridge the gap between academic learning and real enterprise
          engineering. Most graduates struggle because traditional learning focuses heavily on theory
          while modern companies demand practical problem-solving skills.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <header class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-title">Our mission</h2>
          <p class="section-desc">
            We focus on preparing engineers for real environments — not just certifications.
          </p>
        </header>
        <div class="cards-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Hands-on DevOps training</h3>
            <p>Build muscle memory with labs that reflect how teams ship and operate.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Real-world infrastructure exposure</h3>
            <p>Networks, clusters, pipelines, and observability — experienced in context.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>AI-powered operations knowledge</h3>
            <p>Automation, triage, and modern tooling without hype.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Production troubleshooting experience</h3>
            <p>Incidents, rollbacks, and debugging under realistic constraints.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container two-col">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label">Vision</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Industry-ready engineers</h2>
          <p class="section-desc mt-0">
            To build industry-ready DevOps and AI engineers capable of operating modern production
            systems confidently.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="section-label">Mission pillars</p>
          <ul class="list-check">
            <li>Deliver practical engineering education</li>
            <li>Simulate real enterprise scenarios</li>
            <li>Teach AI-assisted operations</li>
            <li>Help students become production-ready</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-band">
          <h2>Ready to go deeper?</h2>
          <p>Explore tracks and labs designed for the way cloud-native teams work today.</p>
          <a href="/courses/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">View courses</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
